    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-8024-accb-fee946e59ccb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Current group formation algorithms often come short on two main problems: uneven group size and inaccessibility of learner carachteristics. Authors propose a genetic-algorithm-based approach divided into 2 modules:",
